+So/CP  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** segment ordering: case, person
+So/PC  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** segment ordering: person, case

!! #### The comparative forms are:
 +Comp !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** РҙР¶СӢРә
 +Superl !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** 

!! #### Numeral tags:
 +Attr +Card !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** 
 +Ord  !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** 
 +Iter !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**  Iterative form expressing number of times
 +Tot   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** 
 +Arab +Rom   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** 
 +Coll 	      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** 

!! #### Quantifiers (numerals)

 +Appr      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**:  Approximative numeral РәР°РІСӮРҫ-РәРҫР»РјРҫ, РәРҫР»РјРҫСҲРәР° *two or three*   NB! do not confuse with Komi case +Apr
 +AssocColl !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**:  -ne- ; avide-
 +Assoc     !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**:  +РјРөР·СӮСҢ
 +Card      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**:  cardinal + NCard
 +ZeroColl      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**:  Zero collective РәРҫРҙРҪСӢСҒ
 +Distr     !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**:  Distributive
 +Iter      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@: Iterative form expressing number of consecutive times; kpv**:  `РәСӢРәСӢСҒСҢ`
 +Mult      !!вүҲ * **@CODE@: Multiplicative adverbs number of times; kpv**:  `РәСӢРә РҝУ§РІ`
 +Coord       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**:  Coordinates, i.e. 65Лҡ36вҖІ8,30вҖі in numerals.lexc
 +Cop       !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**:  this is for copula complement predicate position with pl in -У§СҒСҢ depricated Pred


!! #### Verb tags
 +Ind +Prs +Prt1 +Prt2 +Fut +Imprt    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** tense
 +Sg1 +Sg2 +Sg3 +Pl1 +Pl2 +Pl3 +Du1    !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** person СӮСҚР°-РјРөР°
+1 +2 +3   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**  Final РјРөРҙ РҫРі _so that I/we won't_ 2019-04-06
 +Inf   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** 
 +Ger   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**  Gerund This is used with derivations
+ConNeg +Neg   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** 
+VAbess !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** СӮУ§Рј Participle verbal adjective, see also Der/Abe
+VCar !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** СӮУ§Рі Gerund
+VTer !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** СӮУ§РҙР· Gerund
+Final   !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**  РјРҫРі, РјРҫРҪ, РјРҫР· 'so that I won't'
 +TV !!вүҲ * **@CODE@** 
 +IV !!вүҲ * **@CODE@**
