@U.CONJ-POSS.2ACC@       !!вүҲ | **@CODE@** | POSS = possessive etc.
@U.CONJ-POSS.3ACC@       !!вүҲ | **@CODE@** | POSS = possessive
@U.CONJ-PX.1@            !!вүҲ | **@CODE@** | PX = person
@U.CONJ-PX.2@            !!вүҲ | **@CODE@** | PX = person
@U.CONJ-PX.3@            !!вүҲ | **@CODE@** | PX = person
@C.CONJ-VAL@             !!вүҲ | **@CODE@** | Removal
